object = {'title':'About Us','url':'http://stores.ebay.com.au/Gear-HQ/About-Us.html','content':'<p>	GEAR HQ is an Australian based distributer offering wholesale prices on quality industrial products from around the world. Make sure to check out our store for a comprehensive range of Tools, Rigging, PPE and Industrial Hardware at dirt cheap prices.<br />	<br />	With over 1000+ products from industrial manufacturers locally and internationally, at amazingly low prices, our goal is to have 100% satisfied customers.<br />	<br />	Gear HQ has been trading on eBay since 2007 and has grown from strength to strength.<br />	<br />	Gear HQ is a leading seller of quality industrial products on eBay, and is proudly Australian owned and operated business. We offer the highest standard of service and supply professional quality tools at discounted prices.<br />	<br />	At Gear HQ we provide our customers with quality products at discounted prices, prompt and friendly customer service, 100% satisfaction guaranteed with our 30 day return policy offered on each purchase, fast, reliable and traceable shipping, we only sell brand new and only genuine products and low shipping costs.<br />	<br />	Why are our items discounted? Being a retailer that sells predominantly online, we are able to provide 24-hour 7-days a week online service at a substantially lower cost base than traditional shop front retailers who have to operate with more overheads and expenses.<br />	 <br />	Because we operate on fewer overheads we provide customers with large discounts on all of our products.<br />	<br />	If you can’t find what you need in our eBay shop... Send us an email for a competitive quote on any Tools, Rigging, PPE and Industrial Hardware.<br />	<br />	 <br />	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>Shipping</strong></span><br />	 <br />	We pride ourselves on having the Best Customer Service and we want you to have your Brand New Item(s) as fast as possible. That\'s why we will ship all orders within 1 business day of receiving cleared funds. Making your experience Fast and Hassel Free.<br />	 <br />	Why not check out our latest offers from "Gear HQ" and grab a great quality discount today.<br />	If you can’t find what you need in our eBay shop... Send us an email for a competitive quote on any Tools, Rigging, PPE and Industrial Hardware.<br />	<br />	<strong><span style="font-size:14px;">Returns</span></strong><br />	 <br />	When you buy from Gear HQ store, you buy with confidence. Every piece of equipment we offer is of the highest possible quality… Guaranteed.<br />	 <br />	Why not check out our New Items for sale and take advantage of our discounted flat rate shipping anywhere in Australia.<br />	 <br />	Terms and conditions of returns<br />	 • All items are inspected prior to been shipped, but If you find an item or items to be faulty due to a Manufacturer defect, then simply take a photo of the defected item or items and send it through to us. We will be more than happy to send you a replacement once photos have been received.<br />	 • Buyer will pay for return postage.<br />	 • Items lost or misplaced by Australia Post will be buyer’s responsibility.<br />	 • Once package has been received and seal is intact, then a full refund or exchange of the purchase price will happily be given.<br />	 • If you have any questions then please free to contact us.</p>'};
pages_array.push(object);
object = {'title':'Shipping and Returns','url':'http://stores.ebay.com.au/Gear-HQ/Shipping-and-Returns.html','content':'<div>	<p>		<strong>Shipping</strong></p>	<p>		We pride ourselves on having the Best Customer Service and we want you to have your Brand New Item(s) as fast as possible. That\'s why we will ship all orders within 1 business day of receiving cleared funds. Making your experience Fast and Hassel Free.</p>	<p>		Why not check out our latest offers from "Gear HQ" and grab a great quality discount today.</p>	<p>		<strong>Returns</strong></p>	<p>		When you buy from Gear HQ store, you buy with confidence. Every piece of jewellery we offer is of the highest possible quality ? Guaranteed.</p>	<p>		Why not check out our New Items for sale and take advantag of our discounted flate rate shipping anywhere in Australia.</p>	<p>		<strong>Terms and conditions of returns</strong></p>	<ul>		<li>			All items are inspected prior to been shipped, but If you find an item or items to be faulty due to a Manufactuer defect, then simply take a photo of the defected item or items and send it through to us. We will be more than happy to send you a replacement once photos have been received.</li>	</ul>	<ul>		<li>			Buyer will pay for return postage.</li>	</ul>	<ul>		<li>			Items lost or misplaced by Australia Post will be buyers responsilbilty.</li>	</ul>	<ul>		<li>			Once package has been received and seal is intact, then a full refund or exchange of the purchase price will happily be given.</li>	</ul>	<ul>		<li>			If you have any questions then please free to contact us.</li>	</ul></div><div></div>'};
pages_array.push(object);


